Import payment data from an external source to the Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management app to show payment metrics in relevant dashboards.

Create a CSV file with these fields:
AccountId
Product2Id
Bill_Period_Start
Bill_Period_End
PaymentMode
Invoice_ID
Amount
Currency
Date_of_Payment

Save the CSV file and create the app, then locate the Media_Payment dataset and replace data with the uploaded CSV file.
